lead_paragraph: AC Milan scraped a 1-0 win over third tier Alessandria thanks to a Mario Balotelli penalty, his first goal for four months, in the first leg of their Coppa Italia semi-final on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Milan Scrape Win Over Underdogs Alessandria With Balotelli Penalty
headline.main: Milan Scrape Win Over Underdogs Alessandria With Balotelli Penalty
